snippet: Anastasia Pavlyuchenkova ousted second-seeded Lucie Safarova from the Kremlin Cup, 6-1, 6-7 (2), 6-3, leaving Safarova vulnerable to being left out of the season-ending WTA finals next week in Singapore.
abstract: Anastasia Pavlyuchenkova beats Lucie Safarova at Kremlin Cub tennis tournament; other tennis news noted.
lead_paragraph: Anastasia Pavlyuchenkova ousted second-seeded Lucie Safarova from the Kremlin Cup, 6-1, 6-7 (2), 6-3, leaving Safarova vulnerable to being left out of the season-ending WTA finals next week in Singapore.
